Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此 也不是完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的身高體格來判斷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H313131&\3c&HEDEDED&\pos(1232,280)}年齡身體測定的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H313131&\3c&HEDEDED&\pos(1656,365)}重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H313131&\3c&HEDEDED&\pos(1664,551)}輕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H313131&\3c&HEDEDED&\pos(1686,998)}黑儀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平均體重應該是四十五公斤以上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是實際的體重是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是初中畢業 進入這所高中之前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了一隻螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體重被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就算你不理解也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為被胡亂猜測的話過於麻煩 所以才說的
