Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:54.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@微软雅黑\frz270\pos(1120,179)}下回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:54.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@微软雅黑\frz270\pos(1131,558)}繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.49,0:25:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是火憐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.09,0:25:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是月火
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.98,0:25:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然叫做工蟻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.18,0:25:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼叫的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.02,0:25:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有兩成是在工作的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.97,0:25:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的八成不幹活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.78,0:25:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要提意見
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.01,0:25:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.51,0:25:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工蟻這種名字本來就是強加於人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.67,0:25:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在操縱別人的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.60,0:25:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 又不能叫做偷懶螞蟻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.29,0:25:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來是預告片謎題
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.76,0:25:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎題
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.19,0:25:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到Hit and Beat那就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.82,0:25:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火憐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.57,0:25:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個and表示的記號該怎麼念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.73,0:25:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是問題難 是問題文讓人搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.69,0:25:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.32,0:25:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是&吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.16,0:25:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不通啊
